message.body: Hey Chris, could I still have some bond paper before my interview on Thursday?
Sure, come by my pace around 615 and I'll get you some
I have a writing center staff meeting from 6-7...is there another time before 10 you'll be around?
Not really... Maybe tomorrow after dinner?
Could you leave it somewhere I can pick it up?
I'll be in my room until about 530 if you want some resume paper
